<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Fragment from the left side of a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> columnar <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> front (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.305</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.40</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.43</measure>). On what survives of the left short end part of a draped female figure is visible beside a column at the corner.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the lower part of the front face, above a carved lower edge; there are traces of sculptured decoration above.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>standard forms, Second to third centuries A.D.; <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.02</measure>
</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)
</p>
</div>
